# Plan B Asia — Environment Variables Template
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. Frontend vars (VITE_ prefix): copy to Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables
#   2. Backend secrets: copy to Supabase → Project Settings → Edge Functions → Secrets
#   3. NEVER commit real values — only this template. Real .env.local is gitignored.
#
# Secret vault map: C:\Users\User\Planbasia\memory\context\secrets-vault.md

# ── Frontend (VITE_ prefix — Vite exposes only these to browser) ──
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR_ANON_KEY_PUBLIC_SAFE
VITE_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_YOUR_KEY_PUBLIC
VITE_POSTHOG_KEY=phc_YOUR_KEY_PUBLIC
VITE_POSTHOG_HOST=https://app.posthog.com
VITE_GTM_ID=GTM-YOUR_CONTAINER_ID
# Meta Pixel + TikTok Pixel IDs are hardcoded in src/lib/*Pixel.ts (public IDs)

# ── Backend secrets (Supabase Edge Function Secrets — NEVER frontend) ──
# These lines are for documentation only. Set them at:
# https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/gjbuoyxwujpbaprcrnmg/settings/functions
#
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_YOUR_SECRET
# RESEND_API_KEY=re_YOUR_KEY
# META_CAPI_ACCESS_TOKEN=YOUR_CAPI_TOKEN     # Sprint 4
# TIKTOK_EVENTS_API_TOKEN=YOUR_TIKTOK_TOKEN  # Sprint 4
# SENTRY_DSN=YOUR_SENTRY_DSN                 # Sprint 4
